---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Story received"
  description="Your story was received. A person reviews every submission before anything is published."
>
  <div class="wrap prose">
    <h1>Your story was received</h1>
    <p>
      Thank you. A person on the team reads every submission. Nothing is
      published automatically, and anything that identifies you is scrubbed
      before a story is displayed.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you left contact info, we only use it to check facts with you. It is
      never displayed.
    </p>
    <p>
      You can withdraw your story at any time. The
      <a href="/legal/submission-consent">submission consent</a> page explains
      how.
    </p>
    <p><a class="btn" href="/">Back to the front page</a></p>
  </div>
</Base>
